-- Denizbank says cooperating with Sberbank on 3rd Istanbul airport financing
-- By Evren Ballim
-- Fri Aug 08, 2014 05:45AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Aug 8 (Reuters) - Turkish lender Denizbank <DENIZ.IS>, owned by Sberbank <SBER.MM>, said on Friday it was cooperating with the Russian bank for the financing of Istanbul's third airport.

Denizbank saw no impact on the bank from international sanctions against Russia, Board Chairman Hakan Ates told reporters.